            <h2 class="title uppercase">Helping Start-ups find their voice online</h2>
            <p class="title-sm">YOUR ONE STOP GUY FOR THE JOB</p>
            
            <div class="text">
                <p>I am a Full Stack Web Developer whose sole aim is to bring value to your project, team or business. I enjoy creating elegant designs and architecture for clients and teams. I have a good experience in collaborating with people to make sure I get them their desired outcome. 

                When building out projects, I make sure to focus on the things that will affect your project, team or business positively.  I make sure my designs are </p>

                <ul>
                    <li>User Friendly</li>
                    <li>Elegant</li>
                    <li>Mobile Responsive</li>
                    <li>Fast in Performance</li>
                    <li>Scalable</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
